{"title":"Sniper","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Sniper","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.31](/0.31 \"0.31\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                         |\n| - | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | The sacred weapon of Toth-Mos, first apostle of the god Ashenzari. It grants the wielder a fraction of Ashenzari's own vision, ensuring that every shot will land true. |\n\n[![New sniper.png](/images/5/55/New_sniper.png)](/File:New_sniper.png) ***the +27 heavy crossbow \"Sniper\"***\n\n+27 heavy crossbow (modified [triple crossbow](/Triple_crossbow \"Triple crossbow\"); base delay 25)\n\n[Heavy](/Heavy \"Heavy\") brand  \n[See invisible](/See_invisible \"See invisible\")  \nNever misses\n\n## Desirability\n\n**Sniper**[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1) is essentially the [dark maul](/Dark_maul \"Dark maul\") of ranged weapons: it has an incredible enchantment, but sluggish delay. At 27 skill, you'll have a delay of 1.725 - this equates to a 75% of shooting at 1.7 turns, and 25% of shooting at 1.8. You'll also have a 34.5 base damage weapon enchanted to +27. For overall damage per turn, this is roughly equal to a +9 [branded](/Brand \"Brand\") triple crossbow.\n\nAttacking slow comes with a big risk. For every bolt you shoot, enemies will often get 2 turns to move. Fast enemies, like [orbs of fire](/Orbs_of_fire \"Orbs of fire\"), can move thrice. Be wary of using this against especially fast enemies, or foes with dangerous ranged abilities. In dangerous situations, use [potions of haste](/Potions_of_haste \"Potions of haste\") or [Okawaru](/Okawaru \"Okawaru\")'s Finesse to speed up your shots as much as possible.\n\nOn the flip side, perfect accuracy is valuable against monsters with high EV, like [spriggans](/List_of_spriggans \"List of spriggans\") or [Ereshkigal](/Ereshkigal \"Ereshkigal\"). If nothing else, you can use Sniper as a swapout. Like all weapons, it takes only 0.5 turn to swap from Sniper to a different ranged weapon.\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\"), Sniper was a +9 [vorpal](/Vorpal \"Vorpal\") triple crossbow, with base delay 27.\n- Prior to [0.18](/0.18 \"0.18\"), Sniper had an enchantment of +15 and lacked perfect accuracy.\n- Prior to [0.15](/0.15 \"0.15\"), Sniper was a standard [crossbow](/Crossbow_\\(item\\) \"Crossbow (item)\") with a +15 enchantment and the [vorpal](/Vorpal \"Vorpal\") brand, but it was given a slower-than-normal rate of fire.\n- Prior to [0.14](/0.14 \"0.14\"), Sniper had a +10,+0 enchantment level and the [venom](/Venom \"Venom\") brand.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [art-data.txt:633](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.0/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L633) (0.30.0)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Sniper - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Sniper\",\"wgTitle\":\"Sniper\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":79255,\"wgRevisionId\":79255,\"wgArticleId\":4395,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.31 articles\",\"Unrands\",\"Crossbows\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDa